dc_description_s: This data represents zoning (general) for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2024. [Calumet County zoning delineation that corresponds to the Zoning Ordinance passed in 2009. Zoning Districts: Wetland (W), Exclusive Agricultural Wetland (EAW), Natural Area (NA), Exclusive Agricultural (EA), General Agricultural (GA), Heartland (HL), Small Estate Residential (SE), Single Family Residential-20,000 (SF20), Single Family Residential-10,000 (SF10), High Density Residential (HD), Mixed Use Commercial (MC), Recreational Commercial (RC), Commercial Center (CC), Light Industrial (LI), Industrial (I)]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://gis-calumet.hub.arcgis.com/
